課程概述 Course Description
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course focuses on clarification of a series of crucial yet less-taught concepts and encourages open discussion in class.    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1From Wave Nature of Light to Photonics in Materials2From Wave Nature of Light to Photonics in Materials3Semiconductor Science and Light Emitting Diodes(band structure, p-n junction, LED mechanism, and LED materials)4Semiconductor Science and Light Emitting Diodes(band structure, p-n junction, LED mechanism, and LED materials)5Semiconductor Science and Light Emitting Diodes(band structure, p-n junction, LED mechanism, and LED materials)6Stimulated Emission in Materials7Stimulated Emission in Materials8Stimulated Emission in Materials9Stimulated Emission in Materials10Photodetectors11Photodetectors12Photodetectors13Photodetectors14Photovoltaic Device 15Photovoltaic Device 16Photovoltaic Device 17Polarization and Modulation of Light in Materials 18Polarization and Modulation of Light in Materials  

